<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
  </head>
  <body>    
    <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/home'}) %> 

    <main class="container mx-auto mt-10">
      <section class="hero bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-6">
        <div class="max-w-md mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Explore Climate Solutions</h1>
          <p class="py-6">
            Discover projects addressing climate change across various sectors.
          </p>
          <a href="/solutions/projects" class="btn btn-primary"
            >View All Projects</a
          >
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-10">
        <div>
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img
                class="w-full"
                src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_recycledmetals_0.jpg"
                alt="Abandoned Farmland Restoration"
              />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">"Recycled Metals</h2>
              <p>
                Metals are extracted from nonrenewable ores. Recycled metals
                capitalize on already extracted materialsâ€”making it possible to
                produce goods more efficiently, reduce the need to extract new
                resources, and cut down on energy and water use.
              </p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-end py-6">
                <a href="/solutions/projects/17" class="btn btn-primary"
                  >More Information</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img
                class="w-full"
                src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_ships01.jpg"
                alt="Alternative Cement"
              />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Efficient Ocean Shipping</h2>
              <p>
                Huge volumes of goods are shipped across oceans. Fuel-saving
                ship design, technologies, and practices can trim greenhouse gas
                emissions.
              </p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-end py-6">
                <a href="/solutions/projects/18" class="btn btn-primary"
                  >More Information</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img
                class="w-full"
                src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_improvedmanuremanagement.jpg"
                alt="Bicycle Infrastructure"
              />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Improved Manure Management</h2>
              <p>
                Livestock manure produces methane, a potent greenhouse gas.
                Advanced technologies and practices for managing manure can
                reduce the adverse climate impact of animal agriculture.
              </p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-end py-6">
                <a href="/solutions/projects/20" class="btn btn-primary"
                  >More Information</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
